%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22AOC%20and%20Bernie%20Sanders%20have%20a%20bill%20to%20pause%20AI%20data%20center%20construction.%20Here's%20what's%20in%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sen.%20Bernie%20Sanders%20and%20Rep.%20Alexandria%20Ocasio-Cortez%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c3e6bde98a37a4841f3699%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221236%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bill%20would%20halt%20the%20construction%20of%20new%20AI%20data%20centers%20around%20the%20US%20until%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20national%20safeguards%26quot%3B%20are%20put%20in%20place.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FDavid%20Zalubowski%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBernie%20Sanders%20has%20been%20calling%20for%20a%20nationwide%20moratorium%20on%20new%20AI%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20he%20and%20AOC%20are%20rolling%20out%20a%20bill%20that%20would%20do%20just%20that.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20would%20halt%20new%20data%20center%20construction%20until%20Congress%20passes%20comprehensive%20AI%20regulations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20top%20progressive%20lawmakers%20have%20a%20plan%20to%20bring%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-locations-us-map-ai-boom-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20buildout%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20halt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Bernie%20Sanders%20of%20Vermont%20and%20Democratic%20Rep.%20Alexandria%20Ocasio-Cortez%20of%20New%20York%20are%20introducing%20the%20%26quot%3BArtificial%20Intelligence%20Data%20Center%20Moratorium%20Act%26quot%3B%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20would%20impose%20a%20nationwide%20halt%20on%20the%20new%20construction%20or%20upgrading%20of%20data%20centers%20until%20Congress%20passes%20legislation%20imposing%20new%20regulations%20on%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20regulations%20that%20the%20bill%20says%20would%20need%20to%20be%20included%20for%20the%20moratorium%20to%20be%20lifted%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGovernmental%20review%20and%20approval%20of%20new%20AI%20products%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPolicies%20to%20prevent%20job%20displacement%20due%20to%20AI%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEnsuring%20new%20data%20centers%20don't%20raise%20electric%20bills%20or%20worsen%20climate%20change%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20data%20centers%20are%20built%20by%20union%20workers%20with%20strong%20labor%20standards.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESanders%20first%20called%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbernie-sanders-ai-data-center-construction-moratorium-pause-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoratorium%20on%20AI%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%2C%20and%20the%20idea%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbernie-sanders-ai-data-center-moratorium-reaction-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyet%20to%20gain%20widespread%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Capitol%20Hill.%20It's%20a%20long-shot%2C%20largely%20symbolic%20effort%20aimed%20at%20drawing%20attention%20to%20the%20widespread%20societal%20impacts%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20sit%20back%20and%20allow%20a%20handful%20of%20billionaire%20Big%20Tech%20oligarchs%20to%20make%20decisions%20that%20will%20reshape%20our%20economy%2C%20our%20democracy%20and%20the%20future%20of%20humanity%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanders%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20serious%20public%20debate%20and%20democratic%20oversight%20over%20this%20enormously%20consequential%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESanders's%20push%20for%20an%20AI%20data%20center%20moratorium%20has%20already%20encountered%20strong%20pushback%20from%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20which%20has%20taken%20a%20friendly%20approach%20toward%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20Crypto%20and%20AI%20Czar%20David%20Sacks%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDavidSacks%2Fstatus%2F2001320789279203694%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Sanders's%20idea%20is%20about%20%26quot%3Bstopping%20progress%20completely%20so%20China%20wins%20the%20AI%20race.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecognizing%20that%20data%20centers%20have%20led%20to%20higher%20electric%20bills%20for%20some%20consumers%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20recently%20partnered%20with%20a%20slew%20of%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20to%20sign%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-companies-data-centers-electricity-donald-trump-ratepayer-protection-pledge-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERatepayer%20Protection%20Pledge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20those%20firms%20voluntarily%20agree%20to%20cover%20a%20greater%20share%20of%20their%20energy%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20center%20industry%20is%20also%20pushing%20back%20on%20Sanders%20and%20Ocasio-Cortez.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECy%20McNeill%2C%20Senior%20Director%20of%20Federal%20Affairs%20at%20the%20Data%20Center%20Coalition%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20data%20centers%20%26quot%3Bpower%20modern%20life%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20a%20moratorium%20risks%20%26quot%3Brationing%20access%20to%20digital%20services%2C%20impairs%20our%20global%20competitiveness%2C%20and%20will%20have%20substantial%20impacts%20on%20Americans'%20daily%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faoc-bernie-sanders-introduce-bill-ai-data-center-moratorium-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774451989000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c3e9b058b5806618e7e2dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faoc-bernie-sanders-introduce-bill-ai-data-center-moratorium-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bill%20would%20halt%20the%20construction%20of%20new%20AI%20data%20centers%2