e%20this%20will%20disincentivize%20gaming%20the%20attention%20of%20US%20or%20Japanese%20accounts%20and%20instead%2C%20drive%20diverse%20conversations%20on%20the%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20Bier%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20seems%20like%20a%20good%20idea.%20It's%20also%20one%20that%20builds%20on%20work%20Bier%20had%20done%20previously%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20when%20he%20started%20disclosing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fx-shows-locations-users-about-this-account-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhere%20X%20users%20were%20actually%20based%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffake-twitter-accounts-elon-musk-x-location-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elots%20of%20accounts%20that%20purported%20to%20be%20very%20interested%20in%20American%20politics%20and%20culture%20wars%20were%20run%20by%20people%20outside%20America%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBier's%20plan%20wouldn't%20prevent%20those%20posters%20from%20weighing%20in%20on%20US%20elections%20or%20anything%20else.%20But%20it%20would%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20those%20posters%20to%20make%20money%20doing%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%20it's%20not%20happening%2C%20per%20Musk.%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F2036685311179477401%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWe%20will%20pause%20moving%20forward%20with%20this%20until%20further%20consideration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20an%20X%20user%20who%20was%20complaining%20about%20the%20new%20policy%20early%20Wednesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20have%20been%20news%20to%20Bier%2C%20who%20was%20on%20the%20platform%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F2036685311179477401%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefending%20the%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F2