C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20players%20use%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-most-people-dont-know-about-survivor-fun-facts-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etime%20at%20Ponderosa%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20influence%20the%20competition.%20Rickenbacker%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20was%20still%20in%20%26quot%3Bgame%20mode%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20was%20voted%20off%2C%20so%20he%20advocated%20for%20his%20last%20ally%20on%20the%20island%20and%20eventual%20season%20winner%2C%20Nick%20Wilson.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20still%20playing%20the%20game%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Rickenbacker%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20going%20up%20to%20Goliaths%2C%20you%20know%2C%20trying%20to%20balance%20for%20him%20so%20that%20they%20would%20get%20his%20vote%20at%20the%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20even%20chose%20to%20room%20with%20a%20player%20from%20the%20rival%20tribe%2C%20Dan%20Rengering%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bto%20sway%20him%20to%20get%20Nick's%20vote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20though%20Patel%20said%20she%20didn't%20think%20about%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20vote%20went%20where%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20was%20still%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20bit%20vocal%20with%20the%20other%20members%20of%20the%20jury%26quot%3B%20about%20her%20concerns%20with%20some%20players%20in%20the%20game.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20other%20players%20said%20it's%20hard%20to%20care%20about%20the%20game%20once%20you're%20voted%20out.%20Four-time%20competitor%20(and%20one-time%20champion)%20Tyson%20Apostol%20said%20if%20players%20could%20%26quot%3Bforgo%20your%20jury%20vote%20to%20go%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he'd%20choose%20that%20option%20%26quot%3Bevery%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoehlke%20agreed%20that%20you%20care%20less%20about%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20game%20%26quot%3Bthe%20longer%20you%20are%20in%20Ponderosa.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20hear%20the%20drama%20and%20what's%20going%20on%2C%20but%20you're%20so%20bitter%20about%20not%20winning%2C%26quot%3B%20Boehlke%20told%20BI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPlayers%20often%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20consequences%20of%20overeating%2C%20muscle%20loss%2C%20and%20infections.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222672%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ciera%20Eastin%20and%20Malcolm%20Freberg%20sitting%20on%20a%20log%20with%20some%20smoke%20in%20the%20background%20on%20%26quot%3BSurvivor%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60f8639bfc253600181fa5d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222004%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECiera%20Eastin%20and%20Malcolm%20Freberg%20on%20%26quot%3BSurvivor%3A%20Game%20Changers.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECBS%20Photo%20Archive%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20players%20said%20that%20after%20living%20on%20a%20remote%20island%20with%20little%20food%20for%20weeks%2C%20their%20bodies%20sometimes%20had%20a%20difficult%20time%20adjusting%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworst-and-grossest-things-about-playing-on-survivor-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epost-%26quot%3BSurvivor%26quot%3B%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20players%20told%20BI%20that%20it's%20common%20to%20eat%20yourself%20sick%20at%20Ponderosa.%20Apostol%20said%20he%20had%20to%20take%20medicine%20for%20his%20digestive%20tract%20because%20he%20did%20%26quot%3Bhorrible%20things%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20players%20also%20lose%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20weight%20on%20the%20island%2C%20but%20Freberg%20%E2%80%94%20who%20said%20he%20once%20dropped%2025%20pounds%20in%20a%20single%20season%20%E2%80%94%20said%20his%20biggest%20bodily%20change%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-lost-44lbs-learned-important-lessons-lose-fat-maintain-muscle-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elost%20muscle%20mass%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20work%20out%20like%20I%20was%20when%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%20or%20anything%20like%20that%2C%20but%20I%20can't%20build%20the%20muscle%20mass%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Freberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20had%20skinny%20legs%20and%20now%20they're%20just%20twigs%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20that's%20ever%20going%20to%20come%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20ailments%20can%20require%20extra%20medical%20attention.%20Boehlke%20said%20she%20had%20to%20go%20to%20the%20hospital%20after%20a%20urinary%20tract%20infection%20she%20got%20on%20%26quot%3BSurvivor%3A%20Game%20Changers%26quot%3B%20that%20spread%20to%20her%20kidneys.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20week%20with%20a%20very%20severe%20kidney%20infection%2C%26quot%3B%20Boehlke%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20also%20affecting%20my%20other%20organs%2C%20so%20my%20heart%20was%20in%20a%20weakened%20state.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatel%20also%20said%20she%20went%20to%20the%20hospital%20after%20a%20UTI%20turned%20into%20a%20painful%20bladder%20infection.%20Multiple%20players%20told%20BI%20that%20CBS%20covered%20their%20medical%20costs%20after%20the%20show.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20published%20a%20more%20in-depth%20look%20at%20UTIs%20and%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurvivor-players-health-risks-same-underwear-for-month-utis-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehealth%20risks%20on%20%26quot%3BSurvivor%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20CBS%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20our%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMany%20competitors%20also%20have%20to%20adjust%20mentally.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elaine%20Stott%20looking%20pensive%20in%20a%20closeup%20on%20Survivor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60c11c196d855e00181572bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECBS%20Photo%20Archive%2FGetty%20Ima