0height%3D%5C%221687%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrea%20Boehlke%20on%20%26quot%3BSurvivor%3A%20Game%20Changers.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECBS%20Photo%20Archive%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EViewers%20follow%20along%20with%20the%20heavily%20condensed%20action%20at%20home%20as%20the%20show%20airs%2C%20and%20Boehlke%20said%20%26quot%3Bit's%20easy%20to%20hate%20on%20people%20because%20of%20the%20edit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20a%20pretty%20noncontroversial%20character%20and%20I%20got%20death%20threats%2C%26quot%3B%20Boehlke%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20imagine%20what%20the%20villains%20on%20'Survivor'%20face.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoehlke%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20players%20are%20%26quot%3Bgood%20people%26quot%3B%20in%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20conditions%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20attacks%20on%20your%20character%2C%20looks%2C%20and%20personality%20%26quot%3Bcan%20weigh%20on%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20all%20players%20experience%20that%20backlash.%20Rickenbacker%20said%20he%20was%20going%20to%20film%20a%20Jimmy%20Kimmel-inspired%20%26quot%3BMean%20Tweets%26quot%3B%20video%2C%20but%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20to%20find%20a%20lack%20of%20hate%20messages%20online.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20everything%20prepared%2C%20and%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Hey%2C%20where%20are%20the%20hate%20tweets%3F'%26quot%3B%20Rickenbacker%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20searching%20for%20my%20name%2C%20'Davie%2C'%20'hate%2C'%20'Survivor%2C'%20and%20nothing%20came%20up!'%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStott%20told%20BI%20that%20kids%20tell%20her%20she's%20their%20%26quot%3Bhero%26quot%3B%20and%20send%20her%20things%20in%20the%20mail%20that%20she%20hangs%20on%20her%20refrigerator%20%E2%80%94%20which%20%26quot%3Bmeans%20way%20more%20than%20money.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMany%20%26quot%3BSurvivor%26quot%3B%20players%20walk%20away%20from%20the%20show%20with%20lasting%20friendships.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222924%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elaine%20Stott%20hugging%20Karishma%20Patel%20in%20the%20woods%20on%20survivor%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60c10e806d855e0018157250%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222192%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECBS%20Photo%20Archive%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20players%20said%20that%20they%20formed%20lifelong%20bonds%20with%20some%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurvivor-scenes-that-got-cut-from-the-show-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSurvivor%26quot%3B%20castmates%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERickenbacker%20said%20he%2C%20Wilson%2C%20Gabby%20Pascuzzi%2C%20and%20Christian%20Hubicki%20%26quot%3Bchat%20all%20the%20time%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it's%20important%20to%20have%20friends%20from%20the%20show%20%26quot%3Bwho%20went%20through%20that%20same%20experience.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStott%20told%20BI%20that%20she%20talks%20to%20nearly%20everyone%20from%20her%20season%20and%20that%20she%20invited%20%26quot%3Balmost%20the%20entire%20cast%26quot%3B%20to%20her%20wedding.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatel%2C%20who%20experienced%20some%20%26quot%3Bmaliciousness%26quot%3B%20from%20her%20castmates%20on%20the%20island%2C%20said%20that%20she%20gave%20everyone%20%26quot%3Bthe%20benefit%20of%20the%20doubt%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bgot%20to%20know%20them%20outside%20of%20the%20game.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20very%20fortunately%20was%20able%20to%20forge%20friendships%20with%20people%20that%20seemed%20almost%20impossible%20during%20the%20game%20because%20there%20was%20a%20realization%20%E2%80%94%20'Hey%2C%20you%20know%20what%2C%20I%20wasn't%20myself%20out%20there%2C'%26quot%3B%20Patel%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20you%20acknowledge%20that%20...%20then%20you%20can%20push%20it%20aside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%20%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20Dece