tz%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Money%20Storyteller%20(L)%2C%20and%20Danielle%20Nazinitsky%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Decode%20Real%20Estate.%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Bui%20and%20Luc%C3%ADa%20V%C3%A1zquez%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20solo%20business%20founders%2C%20making%20a%20first%20hire%20can%20be%20risky%20and%20time-consuming.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20has%20helped%20capture%20one%20founder's%20expertise%20into%20a%20workflow%20that%20made%20a%20new%20hire%20more%20effective.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20real-estate%20solopreneur%20was%20able%20to%20add%20a%20contractor%20after%20improving%20her%20firm's%20visibility%20on%20AI%20platforms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20nine%20years%20as%20a%20financial%20strategist%20running%20her%20own%20business%2C%20Katherine%20Pomerantz%20often%20considered%20hiring%20a%20business%20manager%20as%20her%20first%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20put%20off%20the%20adding%20an%20employee%2C%20saying%20that%20she%20struggled%20to%20distill%20her%20expertise%20and%20voice-driven%20client%20communications%20into%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20that%20an%20new%20hire%20could%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20able%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20step-by-step%20workflow%20for%20someone%20else%2C%20I%20just%20don't%20think%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pomerantz%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Money%20Storyteller%2C%20which%20offers%20tax%20and%20financial%20services%20for%20small%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Katherine%20Pomerantz%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2ae0f58b5806618e7dcf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226251%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKatherine%20Pomerantz%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Bui%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20perspective%20changed%20when%20she%20started%20using%20generative%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPomerantz%20and%20another%20founder%2C%20Danielle%20Nazinitsky%20of%20Decode%20Real%20Estate%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20generative%20AI%20has%20helped%20them%20make%20effective%20first%20hires%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20scale%20their%20small%20businesses%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fthe-ai-powered-solopreneur%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20AI-Powered%20Solopreneur%3C%2Fa%3E%20series%20explores%20how%20solo%20business%20owners%20use%20AI%20to%20drive%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220f9f459b-d3cf-4d12-a1cc-c92e8e57a678%5C%22%3EAI%20can%20help%20streamline%20employee%20processes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPomerantz%20started%20using%20ChatGPT%20for%20her%20business%20about%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Quickly%2C%20she%20came%20to%20view%20the%20generative%20AI%20platform%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsecond%20brain%2C%26quot%3B%20using%20the%20technology%20to%20streamline%20administrative%20and%20organizational%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20helped%20her%20reverse-engineer%20her%20strategic%20thinking%20into%20day-to-day%20processes.%20Pomerantz%20fed%20client%20call%20recordings%2C%20emails%2C%20brainstorming%20sessions%2C%20and%20other%20material%20into%20the%20model%2C%20which%20helped%20her%20identify%20patterns%20in%20her%20workflow.%20Soon%2C%20she%20had%20procedures%20that%20others%20could%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Pomerantz%20hired%20two%20employees%3A%20an%20administrator%20in%20the%20US%20and%20a%20bookkeeper%20in%20the%20Philippines.%20She%20said%20that%20they%20help%20her%20get%20twice%20as%20much%20work%20done%20as%20she%20did%20as%20a%20solo%20operator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20more%20clients%2C%20and%20are%20meeting%20all%20deadlines%20well%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20Pomerantz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225971%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Katherine%20Pomerantz%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2ae465b58f1f0f93369a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%227961%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKatherine%20Pomerantz%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Bui%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20helping%20establish%20standard%20operating%20procedures%2C%20Pomerantz%20said%20she%20uses%20ChatGPT%20to%20create%20documents%20that%20detail%20her%20decision-making.%20Now%2C%20when%20a%20client%20emails%20with%20a%20question%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20whether%20to%20use%20a%20Roth%20IRA%20%E2%80%94%20Pomerantz's%20administrator%20can%20ask%20AI%20to%20provide%20a%20detailed%20overview%20of%20when%20Pomerantz%20would%20recommend%20a%20particular%20financial%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Pomerantz%20will%20discuss%20key%20decisions%20with%20the%20client%2C%20but%20using%20AI%20and%20her%20administrator%20to%20organize%20information%20in%20advance%20allows%20her%20to%20save%20time%20while%20delivering%20prompt%2C%20in-depth%20responses%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20makes%20her%20clients%20feel%20like%20they're%20always%20getting%20a%20high%20level%20of%20service%2C%20without%20requiring%20more%20working%20hours%20from%20Pomerantz.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20them%20to%20feel%20like%20they%20get%20a%20lot%20more%20of%20my%20time%20than%20they%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d4f4b26-eec9-493a-ba23-1271c910582a%5C%22%3EGenerating%20leads%20using%20AI%20referrals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDanielle%20Nazinitsky%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20boutique%20New%20York%20City%20real%20estate%20firm%20Decode%20Real%20Estate%2C%20also%20found%20generative%20AI%20useful%20for%20scaling%20her%20business%20and%20bringing%20on%20new%20hires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20ChatGPT%20has%20acted%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20referral%20engine%26quot%3B%20for%20her%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20inbound%20leads%2C%20Nazinitsky%20said%20she%20discovered%20that%20some%20prospects%20were%20finding%20her%20name%20via%20ChatGPT.%20To%20build%20on%20this%20momentum%20and%20steer%20clients%20toward%20her%20company%20brand%2C%20she%20retained%20a%20GEO%20firm%20to%20boost%20Decode's%20brand%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225635%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Danielle%20Nazinitsk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2aeca58b5806618e7dcfb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223757%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDanielle%20Nazinitsk%3Cp%3ELuc%C3%ADa%20V%C3%A1zquez%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20learned%20that%20to%20reinforce%20her%20standing%20in%20GEO%20results%2C%20she%20needed%20to%20do%20more%20brand%20blog%20posts%2C%20and%20to%20encourage%20her%20clients%20to%20leave%20reviews%20on%20Google.%20Nazinitsky%20used%20AI%20in%20part%20to%20help%20bolster%20her%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENazinitsky%20said%20that%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20her%20GEO-related%20growth%2C%20she%20had%20the%20resources%20to%20hire%20a%20second%20broker%20six%20months%20ago.%20As%20with%20most%20real%20estate%20brokerages%2C%20her%20second%20broker%20is%20a%20contractor%2C%20not%20a%20full-time%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226664%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Danielle%20Nazinitsk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2af17e98a37a4841f3097%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224442%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDanielle%20Nazinitsk%3Cp%3ELuc%C3%ADa%20V%C3%A1zquez%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20using%20AI%20to%20market%20her%20business%2C%20Nazinitsky%20said%20that%20it's%20been%20just%20as%20important%20to%20learn%20when%20she%20shouldn't%20use%20AI.%20She%20said%20she%20pays%20professional%20contractors%20to%20write%20press%20releases%2C%20handle%20branding%2C%20and%20oversee%20client%20transactions.%3