k%20Zuckerberg%20has%20pushed%20Meta%20to%20become%20more%20efficient.%3Cp%3EBRENDAN%20SMIALOWSKI%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20began%20laying%20off%20hundreds%20of%20employees%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20has%20made%20several%20rounds%20of%20layoffs%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20it%20has%20sought%20to%20become%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Meta%20has%20continued%20to%20pour%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20began%20laying%20off%20hundreds%20of%20employees%20across%20the%20company%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20and%20LinkedIn%20posts%20from%20affected%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20cuts%20affected%20employees%20in%20Reality%20Labs%2C%20Facebook%2C%20recruiting%2C%20sales%2C%20and%20global%20operations%2C%20the%20source%20familiar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20handful%20of%20employees%20who%20worked%20in%20Reality%20Labs%20and%20recruitment%20announced%20on%20LinkedIn%20that%20their%20roles%20had%20been%20eliminated%2C%20according%20to%20posts%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTeams%20across%20Meta%20regularly%20restructure%20or%20implement%20changes%20to%20ensure%20they're%20in%20the%20best%20position%20to%20achieve%20their%20goals.%20Where%20possible%2C%20we%20are%20finding%20other%20opportunities%20for%20employees%20whose%20positions%20may%20be%20impacted%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20employed%20nearly%2079%2C000%20people%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20meaning%20the%20cuts%20reflect%20a%20small%20percentage%20of%20its%20workforce.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Meta%20asked%20some%20managers%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-weighing-major-layoffs-as-it-pours-billions-into-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20prepare%20cost-cutting%20plans%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20senior%20employees%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Some%20Meta%20employees%20in%20the%20company's%20wearables%20and%20ads%20units%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-employees-work-remotely-email-layoffs-hr-wfh-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereceived%20a%20message%20on%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E%20instructing%20them%20to%20work%20from%20home%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20two%20sources%20who%20received%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReuters%20first%20reported%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20the%20company%20was%20considering%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20layoffs%20reflect%20a%20growing%20reality%20across%20Big%20Tech%3A%20costly%20AI%20investment%20is%20coming%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20some%20employee%20roles.%20This%20round%20of%20cost%20cutting%20comes%20as%20Meta%20pours%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20AI%20infrastructure%20and%20building%20teams%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-overhaul-mark-zuckerberg-year-intensity-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20top%20AI%20talent%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20has%20also%20been%20promoting%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20internally.%20Andrew%20Bosworth%2C%20Meta's%20CTO%2C%20told%20staff%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20would%20take%20over%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3BAI%20for%20Work%26quot%3B%20initiative%2C%20an%20effort%20to%20increase%20the%20company's%20adoption%20of%20AI%20tools%20internally%2C%20according%20to%20a%20memo%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20and%20first%20reported%20by%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20many%20of%20you%20I've%20been%20captivated%20by%20the%20power%20AI%20has%20to%20transform%20our%20company%20and%20eager%20to%20unlock%20its%20power%20for%20each%20individual%20and%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Boz%20wrote%20in%20the%20not