ublished%22%3A1774447109000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129803423%2Cimgsize-104654.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fassam-assembly-election-2026-swot-analysis-can-himanta-sarma-retain-power-or-will-gaurav-gogois-debut-shift-the-tide-bpf-agp-ajp-cpm-aiudf-bjp-congress-raijor-dal%2Farticleshow%2F129797273.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Assam's%20political%20landscape%20is%20heating%20up%20alongside%20spring%20festivities%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20aiming%20for%20a%20solo%20majority%20against%20a%20resurgent%20Congress.%20Key%20contests%20include%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20versus%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20while%20issues%20like%20identity%2C%20infiltration%2C%20and%20development%20shape%20the%20electoral%20battleground.%20Post-delimitation%20changes%20add%20another%20layer%20to%20this%20defining%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22AASTHA%20JHA%20AND%20KANCHAN%20YADAV%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Family%20dinners%20are%20hard%20for%202%20working%20parents%20to%20coordinate.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20finally%20found%20a%20way%20to%20divide%20the%20work.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228073%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20fridge%20door%20is%20decorated%20with%20a%20picture%2C%20a%20calendar%20and%20a%20grocery%20list.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c138a458b5806618e7d55e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225202%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20she%20and%20her%20kitchen%20don't%20work%20well%20together%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20She%20said%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20still%20found%20a%20way%20to%20divide%20the%20load%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20making%20dinner%20for%20their%20family%20of%20six.%3Cp%3ECatLane%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWith%20two%20working%20parents%20and%20four%20kids%2C%20mealtime%20is%20always%20a%20little%20hectic%20in%20our%20house.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20very%20different%20styles%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20so%20we%20try%20to%20keep%20our%20distance.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20divide%20the%20work%20into%20manageable%20tasks%2C%20including%20planning%20and%20shopping%2C%20to%20suit%20our%20strengths.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20my%20husband%2C%20but%20cooking%20together%20is%20not%20something%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-divides-household-labor-husband-shops-and-cooks-wife-cleans-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eour%20marriage%20can%20survive%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20can%20admittedly%20get%20a%20little%20tricky%20at%20mealtime%20in%20our%20house.%20With%20two%20working%20parents%20and%20four%20kids%2C%20evenings%20are%20always%20hectic.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquick-one-pot-dinner-recipes-from-professional-meal-planner-mom%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFamily%20dinners%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20very%20important%20to%20us%2C%20and%20we%20do%20everything%20we%20can%20to%20make%20sure%20all%20six%20of%20us%20are%20around%20the%20table%20for%20quality%20time%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20arises%20that%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20very%20different.%20I%20am%20highly%20organized%2C%20yet%20I%20never%20follow%20a%20recipe%20to%20a%20T.%20My%20husband%20is%20analytical%2C%20and%20he%20meticulously%20follows%20every%20recipe%20step%20by%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%20Accomplishing%20the%20family%20dinner%20task%20was%20a%20marital%20nightmare%20until%20we%20decided%20to%20divide%20and%20conquer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-doing-his-and-her-household-chores-doesnt-work-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eour%20own%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20work%20together%20on%20single%20tasks%20until%20they%20were%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1b34f9b-a5e8-438e-a7c1-9d336637ccc1%5C%22%3EI'm%20the%20planner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20plan%20all%20our%20family's%20meals.%20I%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20meal%20rotation%20schedule%20after%20a%20long%20family%20meeting%20about%20dietary%20preferences%20and%20recipe%20likes%20and%20dislikes.%20Now%20I%20have%20a%20four-week%20meal%20plan%20that%20takes%20all%20the%20guesswork%20out%20of%20the%20age-old%20question%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20we%20having%20for%20dinner%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20decided%20we%20would%20aim%20to%20cook%20four%20to%20five%20times%20a%20week%2C%20sometimes%20eating%20the%20same%20meal%20two%20nights%20in%20a%20row%20to%20make%20things%20a%20little%20easier%20on%20us.%20On%20weekends%2C%20we%20will%20usually%20plan%20to%20make%20a%20meal%20on%20Friday%20night%20for%20dinner%2C%20then%20the%20leftovers%20for%20lunch%20on%20Saturday.%20These%20ideas%20aren't%20groundbreaking%2C%20but%20having%20them%20set%20as%20part%20of%20our%20overall%20plan%20for%20the%20week%20means%20we're%20more%20likely%20to%20stick%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20pose%20together.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c13c1ce98a37a4841f292b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20admits%20that%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20don't%20work%20well%20together%20in%20the%20kitchen%20due%20to%20their%20different%20styles%20of%20cooking.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Rachel%20Garlinghouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f71efd9-37e3-46ef-8d9b-7f6784580134%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20husband%20does%20all%20the%20grocery%20shopping%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBelieve%20it%20or%20not%2C%20my%20husband%20enjoys%20the%20routine%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-up-to-80-percent-on-groceries-