ed%20up%20the%20conflicting%20messages%20the%20market%20is%20receiving.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20if%20one%20can't%20trust%20US%20or%20Iranian%20comments%20and%20post%2C%20then%20one%20should%20rely%20on%20(the%20only)%20relevant%20fact%20-%20is%20oil%20going%20through%20Hormuz%3F%20Answer%20is%3A%20NO.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20reports%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20proposal%2C%20Kolanovic%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20relatively%20easy%20to%20talk%20down%20oil%20futures%20prices%2C%20but%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20talk%20up%20level%20of%20fuel%20in%20tanks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-stock-market-today-ceasefire-iran-war-trump-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774445882000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c3de60e98a37a4841f364b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-stock-market-today-ceasefire-iran-war-trump-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Investors%20cheered%20reports%20of%20a%20plan%20to%20end%20the%20Iran%20war.%20Stocks%20rallied%20and%20oil%20prices%20tumbled%2C%20though%20some%20market%20pros%20remained%20cautious.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nbuchanan%40insider.com%20(Naomi%20Buchanan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-stock-market-today-ceasefire-iran-war-trump-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20took%20a%20pay%20cut%20so%20I%20could%20live%20a%20calmer%20life.%20It%20was%20worth%20it%2C%20but%20affording%20city%20life%20became%20more%20difficult.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226301%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20facing%20a%20building%20in%20london%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c311585b58f1f0f9336d66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20struggled%20to%20live%20in%20London%20after%20taking%20a%20pay%20cut.%3Cp%3EKarl%20Hendon%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20life%20was%20becoming%20all%20about%20work%2C%20and%20I%20struggled%20to%20keep%20up%2C%20so%20I%20took%20a%20pay%20cut.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20got%20my%20life%20back%20instantly%2C%20but%20I%20struggled%20to%20afford%20London%20and%20had%20to%20make%20tough%20decisions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tradeoffs%20were%20difficult%2C%20but%20I%20would%20definitely%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20of%20my%20career%2C%20I%20was%20very%20good%20at%20earning%20money%20and%20very%20bad%20at%20enjoying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20years%20in%20high-pressure%20roles%3A%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions%20in%20Mexico%2C%20a%20hedge%20fund%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleave-nyc-miami-retire-early-saving-unexpected-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20capital%20markets%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20paper%2C%20the%20trajectory%20looked%20impressive.%20In%20practice%2C%20the%20life%20behind%20it%20felt%20increasingly%20hollow.%20I%20was%20billing%20hours%20I%20did%20not%20have.%20The%20hustle%20life%20was%20killing%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it.%20I%20took%20a%20break%20from%20life%2C%20recharged%20and%20reconnected%20with%20myself%2C%20and%20transitioned%20into%20a%20more%20balanced%20life.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-seeker-landed-job-cold-emailing-the-ceo-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elanded%20a%20new%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20came%20with%20a%20significant%20pay%20cut.%20I%20was%20making%20a%20third%20less%20than%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20itself%20felt%20romantic%2C%20but%20what%20no%20one%20prepared%20me%20for%20was%20what%20came%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22013a85d6-667f-47fa-a908-2ba882b98426%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20couldn't%20comfortably%20afford%20life%20in%20London%20anymore%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20making%20the%20decision%2C%20I%20built%20a%20careful%20budget.%20I%20accounted%20for%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-luxury-rents-have-gone-up-new-york-london-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELondon%20rent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20utilities%2C%20groceries%2C%20transport%2C%20and%20the%20occasional%20dinner%20out.%20It%20was%20the%20kind%20of%20spreadsheet%20that%20gives%20you%20confidence%20because%20it%20looks%20thorough%20and%20rational.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20failed%20to%20properly%20account%20for%20was%20the%20texture%20of%20daily%20life%20in%20an%20expensive%20city%20like%20London%20when%20you%20are%20no%20longer%20earning%20a%20salary%20that%20absorbs%20every%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20costs%20I%20had%20not%20modeled%20were%20rarely%20dramatic.%20They%20were%20cumulative%3A%20a%20weekend%20trip%20you%20do%20not%20want%20to%20skip%2C%20a%20dinner%20with%20friends%20you%20cannot%20easily%20split%20differently.%20a%20birthday%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-usa-rail-pass-what-to-know-surprises-frequent-traveler-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrain%20ticket%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20flight%20home.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20these%20things%20feels%20extravagant%2C%20but%20together%20they%20quietly%20reshape%20the%20financial%20equation.%20The%20gap%20between%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20afford%20this%20city%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20afford%20this%20city%20comfortably%26quot%3B%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20wider%20than%20I%20had%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20psychological%20dimension%20to%20earning%20less%20that%20I%20underestimated.%20Not%20shame%2C%20exactly.%20I%20had%20already%20made%20peace%20with%20the%20title%20change%20before%20accepting%20the%20role.%20But%20there%20was%20a%20subtle%20awareness%20of%20constraint%20that%20had%20not%20existed%20before.%20Small%20decisions%20carried%20slightly%20more%20weight%2C%20and%20I%20noticed%20prices%20in%20ways%20I%20had%20not%20previously.%20It%20was%20not%20a%20crisis%2C%20just%20a%20different%20relationship%20with%20money%2C%20and%20one%20that%20took%20time%20to%20recalibrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e68caa83-3527-40ef-9687-ab099a9e8519%5C%22%3EThe%20pay%20cut%20influenced%20decisions%20that%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20my%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%20I%20made%20the%20transition%2C%20I%20also%20decided%20to%20move%20in%20with%20my%20girlfriend.%20It%20was%20a%20natural%20step%20in%20our%20relationship%2C%20but%20it%20also%20meant%20thinking%20more%20deliberately%20about%20how%20we%20structured%20our%20finances%20as%20a%20couple.%20Conversations%20about%20rent%2C%20expenses%2C%20and%20long-term%20plans%20became%20more%20concrete%20when%20I%20knew%20my%20income%20looked%20different%20from%20what%20it%20had%20been%20a%20year%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20affected%20how%20I%20approached%20larger%20decisions%20about%20stability.%20In%20my%20previous%20roles%2C%20I%20rarely%20thought%20twice%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-purchases-financial-risks-economic-uncertainty-real-estate-careers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20uncertainty%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20my%20salary%20provided%20a%20large%20cushion.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20transition%2C%20I%20became%20more%20conscious%20of%20building%20that%20sense%20of%20security%20in%20other%20ways.%20I%20paid%20closer%20attention%20to%20savings%2C%20upcoming%20expenses%2C%20and%20how%20much%20flexibility%20I%20actually%20had%20to%20make%20future%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20approach%20to%20travel%20changed%2C%20too.%20Instead%20of%20saying%20yes%20to%20every%20trip%2C%20I%20started%20choosing%20destinations%20more%20deliberately%2C%20prioritizing%20fewer%20trips%20that%20felt%20meaningful%20rather%20than%20frequent%20spontaneous%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20smaller%20aspects%20of%20my%20daily%20life%20shifted%20slightly.%20I%20became%20more%20deliberate%20about%20how%20I%20spent%20my%20time%20and%20money%20together.%20Spontaneous%20plans%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-keep-restaurant-industry-afloat-survey-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edinners%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20small%20purchases%20were%20not%20things%20I%20avoided%2C%20but%20they%20were%20things%20I%20considered%20more%20carefully%20than%20before.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20these%20changes%20was%20dramatic%20on%20its%20own%2C%20but%20together%20they%20reshaped%20the%20rhythm%20of%20my%20daily%20life%20in%20ways%20I%20had%20not%20anticipated%20when%20I%20first%20made%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2227d816e8-7080-43aa-b5b3-bdf21f99731b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20I%20would%20still%20do%20it%20again%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20these%20adjustments%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquarterly-earnings-proposal-sec-accountants-lawyer-investor-relations-jobs-impact-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20trade-offs%3C%2Fa%3E%20ultimately%20added%20up%20to%20one%20simple%20thing%3A%20a%20life%20that%20feels%20recognizably%20my%20own.%20That%20might%20sound%20modest%2C%20but%20after%20years%20of%20structuring%20my%20life%20around%20other%20people's%20expectations%20of%20success%2C%20it%20feels%20significant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20mornings%20now.%20Not%20the%20frantic%2C%20coffee-while-answering-emails%20kind%2C%20but%20actual%20time%20before%20the%20day%20begins%20that%20belongs%20to%20me.%20I%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20my%20partner%2C%20and%20I%20have%20started%20to%20get%20to%20k