get%20in%20the%20car%20and%20drive%20there%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20that's%20exactly%20what%20they%20did%2C%20making%20the%20trip%20by%20car%20in%20under%2010%20hours%20each%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225349%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20American%20woman%20posing%20with%20the%20Barcelona%20skyline.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c365dee98a37a4841f3550%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223566%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHillary%20LaReau%20typically%20travels%20several%20times%20a%20year%2C%20but%20for%20her%20most%20recent%20trip%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20drive%20from%20Colorado%20to%20visit%20family%20in%20Oklahoma%20instead%20of%20flying%20as%20she%20normally%20would.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Hilary%20LaReau.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229bf5f919-55c7-4c30-917c-4a618552acb3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20spontaneous%20mini-break%20is%20under%20threat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20airfares%20rise%20and%20TSA%20lines%20spike%20unpredictably%2C%20many%20US%20travelers%20are%20finding%20spontaneous%20trips%20either%20too%20expensive%20or%20just%20too%20risky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspent-four-hours-at-tsa-jfk-the-situation-felt-dangerous-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravelers%20are%20missing%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20having%20to%20sleep%20in%20the%20airport%20because%20of%20long%20delays%20in%20security%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmily%20Calandriello%2C%20an%20NYC%20resident%20who%20was%20traveling%20with%20her%20husband%20from%20JFK%20Airport%20to%20Costa%20Rica%20this%20week%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20missed%20her%20flight%20after%20nearly%20getting%20caught%20in%20what%20she%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bstampede%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20security%20line.%20She%20ended%20up%20staying%20the%20night%20in%20the%20airport%20and%20taking%20a%20flight%20out%20the