rity-quota-admission-case-he-dared-to-call-my-brother-question-order-chief-justice-surya-kants-contempt-warning-11264681%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbuddhist-medical-college-minority-quota-admission-case-he-dared-to-call-my-brother-question-order-chief-justice-surya-kants-contempt-warning-11264681%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTube%20shows%20are%20closing%20in%20on%20traditional%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20fast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Salish%20Matter%20and%20her%20dad%2C%20Jordan%2C%20are%20among%20a%20growing%20handful%20of%20YouTubers%20making%20TV-like%20shows.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2ed7a58b5806618e7df42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESalish%20Matter%20and%20her%20dad%2C%20Jordan%2C%20are%20among%20a%20growing%20handful%20of%20YouTubers%20making%20TV-like%20shows.%3Cp%3ERodin%20Eckenroth%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Nickelodeon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Spotter%20report%20says%20creators%20are%20starting%20to%20make%20TV-like%20shows%20at%20a%20scale%20similar%20to%20legacy%20TV.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Amazon-backed%20startup%20estimated%20the%20size%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bcreator%20TV%26quot%3B%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESpotter%2C%20like%20YouTube%2C%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20convince%20advertisers%20to%20shift%20spending%20toward%20creators.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fcreator-economy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECreator%20entertainment%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20drawing%20closer%20to%20traditional%20TV%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20new%20report%20makes%20the%20case%20for%20advertisers%20to%20shift%20their%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20Spotter%2C%20shared%20exclusively%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20says%20there%20are%20now%20roughly%206%2C600%20%26quot%3Bcreator%20TV%26quot%3B%20channels%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20defined%20by%20long-form%20episodes%20(22%2B%20minutes)%2C%20consistent%20release%20schedules%2C%20and%20meaningful%20audiences.%20Collectively%2C%20these%20shows%20generated%20an%20estimated%2026%20billion%20hours%20of%20US%20viewing%20in%202025%2C%20with%20more%20than%20half%20of%20that%20on%20connected%20TVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpotter%20is%20an%20Amazon-backed%20startup%20that%20licenses%20creator%20content%20and%20works%20with%20some%20of%20YouTube's%20biggest%20stars%2C%20like%20Kinigra%20Deon%20and%20dad-and-daughter%20team%20Jordan%20and%20Salish%20Matter.%20It%20also%20runs%20an%20ad%20business%20connecting%20brands%20with%20creators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpotter%20estimated%20that%20these%20creator%20TV%20shows%20carry%20about%202.4%20minutes%20of%20ads%20per%20half%20hour%2C%20less%20than%20linear%20and%20streaming%20TV's%20ad%20loads.%20That%20could%20mean%20ads%20there%20have%20a%20better%20chance%20of%20standing%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20the%20creator%20TV%20universe%20is%20comparable%20to%20the%20US%20TV%20market%20in%20terms%20of%20number%20of%20shows%20and%20episodes%2C%20with%20TV%20having%202%2C280%20active%20shows%20and%2094%2C000%20annual%20new%20episodes%2C%20excluding%20local%20news.%20However%2C%20Spotter's%20estimate%20of%20time%20spent%20on%20creator%20TV%20is%20dwarfed%20by%20the%20time%20people%20spend%20streaming%20traditional%20TV%2C%20according%20to%20several%20prominent%20industry%20trackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20single%20industry%20standard%20for%20measuring%20views%20in%20the%20creator%20economy.%20To%20estimate%20view%20time%2C%20Spotter%20used%20data%20from%20its%20creator%20partners%20that%20met%20its%20definition%20of%20creator%20TV.%20It%20stressed%20that%20the%2026%20billion%20US%20hours%20watched%20figure%20should%20be%20read%20as%20a%20directional%2C%20not%20a%20precise%2C%20measurement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1d1f2f1-fc4d-4087-925b-7fa5d86e2145%5C%22%3EAdvertising%20lags%20the%20growing%20creator%20audience%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpotter's%20main%20argument%20is%20that%20brands%20that%20ignore%20the%20%26quot%3Bcreator%20TV%26quot%3B%20opportunity%20risk%20wasting%20precious%20ad%20dollars%20and%20falling%20behind%20viewing%20patterns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20category%20within%20creators%20that%20delivers%20the%20highest%20amount%20of%20attention%20that%20should%20not%20be%20ignored%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aaron%20DeBevoise%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Spotter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20message%20echoes%20those%20of%20YouTube%2C%20which%20wants%20to%20capture%20a%20larger%20share%20of%20the%20ad%20market.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-expands-tv-viewing-new-creator-tools-rival-disney-netflix-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20especially%20craves%3C%2Fa%3E%20TV%20ad%20budgets%2C%20which%20represent%20top-tier%20brand%20spending.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-not-netflix-is-big-threat-to-hollywood-analysis-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYouTube%20has%20gobbled%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20bigger%20share%20of%20the%20TV%20viewing%20pie%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20advertisers%20haven't%20increased%20their%20spending%20proportionately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvertisers%20may%20pay%20%247%20to%20%2410%20to%20reach%201%2C000%20views%20on%20YouTube%2C%20which%20could%20put%20their%20ad%20on%20TV-style%20content%20and%20short-form%20video%20alike%2C%20while%20other%20TV%20platforms%20command%20%2415%20and%20up%2C%20DeBevoise%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20advertisers%20historically%20treated%20YouTube%20as%20digital%20media%20or%20social%20video%2C%20separate%20from%20their%20TV%20ad%20budgets.%20Digital%20video%20hasn't%20been%20measured%20at%20the%20program%20level%20the%20way%20TV%20is.%20Creator%20videos%20also%20vary%20in%20degree%20of%20brand%20suitability%20and%20offer%20limited%20ability%20to%20do%20large-scale%20buys.%20Much%20of%20%26quot%3Bcreator%20TV%26quot%3B%20is%20unscripted%20and%20lacks%20the%20prestige%20TV%20quality%20that%20some%20advertisers%20crave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAudiences%20are%20watching%20more%20video%20than%20ever%2C%20but%20advertisers%20are%20still%20catching%20up%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20authenticity%20and%20entertainment%2C%20not%20polish%20alone%2C%20are%20what%20define%20quality%20TV%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Toni%20Box%2C%20EVP%20of%20brand%20experience%20and%20media%20activation%20at%20Stagwell's%20Assembly%20Global.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Matter%20says%20the%20Spotter%20numbers%20are%20just%20the%20start.%20To%20him%2C%20the%20real%20story%20is%20the%20parasocial%20relationship%20fans%20have%20with%20YouTube%20stars%20like%20his%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20that%20there's%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20people%20trust%20creators%20more%20than%20they%20trust%20a%20traditional%20TV%20show%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246c46de8-1fb2-429b-a118-a3bcff867927%5C%22%3EThe%20ad-creator%20gap%20is%20narrowing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMarketers%20aren't%20standing%20still.%20Many%20have%20been%20adapting%20as%20audiences%20shift%20from%20linear%20TV%20to%20digital%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-tv-ad-budget-google-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20that%20more%20ad%20dollars%20are%20flowing%20to%20YouTube%20from%20TV%20as%20advertisers%20differentiate%20less%20between%20the%20two.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreator-influencer-ad-spend-37-billion-marketing-growth-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2025%20IAB%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20ad%20spenders%20found%20that%20creators%20are%20more%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmust-buy%26quot%3B%20than%20other%20emerging%20ad%20categories%2C%20such%20as%20connected%20TV%20and%20commerce%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-ad-revenue-disney-nbc-paramount-wbd-warner-bros-streaming-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube's%20ad%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20%2440.4%20billion%20in%202025%2C%20now%20exceeds%20that%20of%20its%20four%20largest%20traditional%20media%20competitors%20combined%2C%20according%20to%20analysts%20at%20MoffettNathanson.%20More%20than%20half%20of%20US%20YouTube%20campaigns%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202025%20were%20attributed%20to%20TV%20screens%2C%20per%20Tinuiti.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20measurement%20front%2C%20Comscore%20is%20now%20tracking%20long-form%20content%20on%20YouTube%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.advanced-television.com%2F2026%2F01%2F07%2Fspotter-partners-with-comscore%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunder%20a%20partnership%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Spotter%20announced%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20are%20also%20getting%20harder%20to%20pigeonhole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETop%20YouTuber%20MrBeast%20has%20jumped%20into%20premium%20streaming%2C%20with%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-prime-renews-mrbeasts-beast-games-for-more-seasons-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBeast%20Games%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20competition%20show%20on%20Amazon's%20Prime%20Video.%20Netflix%20and%20other%20TV%20streamers%20are%20picking%20up%20other%20creators%20as%20well%2C%20including%20Ms.%20Rachel%20and%20Mark%20Rober.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotter-report-youtube-creator-shows-approaching-traditional-tv-size-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774437001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2ed7a58b5806618e7df42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotter-report-youtube-cre