D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c31d70e98a37a4841f34aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22615%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHindustan%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMarkets%20are%20fixated%20on%20the%20reopening%20of%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20decision%20to%20postpone%20strikes%20has%20sent%20stocks%20soaring%20and%20oil%20plunging.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20maps%20three%20scenarios%20shaping%20oil%20and%20investor%20strategy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20global%20markets%20right%20now%2C%20the%20reopening%20of%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20is%20pretty%20much%20the%20only%20game%20in%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20attacks%20from%20Iran%20seen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-strikes-qatari-lng-plant-surge-in-oil-gas-prices-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethreatening%20flows%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20the%20strait%20have%20resulted%20in%20an%20oil-price%20spike.%20When%20President%20Trump%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20US%20would%20postpone%20strikes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-futures-oil-price-iran-trump-productive-talks-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estocks%20soared%20and%20oil%20plunged%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20optimism%20that%20tankers%20would%20finally%20get%20a%20green%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20comes%20back%20to%20the%20critical%2C%20roughly%20100-mile%20passage%2C%20which%20processes%20one-third%20of%20the%20world's%20crude%20flows.%20The%20oil%20market%20has%20already%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiea-oil-iran-war-historic-disruption-global-energy-markets-trump-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisrupted%20to%20a%20historic%20degree%3C%2Fa%3E.%20How%20much%20longer%20the%20strait%20stays%20closed%20will%20determine%20how%20stark%20the%20fallout%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20created%20a%20difficult%20situation%20for%20investors%2C%20given%20how%20sensitive%20and%20volatile%20to%20new%20updates%20markets%20have%20proven%20to%20be.%20How%20the%20strait%20gets%20resolved%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20ever%20does%20%E2%80%94%20will%20have%20ramifications%20for%20all%20sorts%20of%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20Morgan%20Stanley%20comes%20in.%20Economists%20and%20equity%20strategists%20at%20the%20firm%20teamed%20up%20to%20lay%20out%20the%20three%20most%20plausible%20scenarios%20for%20what%20happens%20with%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20and%20how%20investors%20should%20allocate%20their%20portfolios%20in%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScenario%201%3A%20De-escalation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOutcome%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3ENormal%20passage%20resumes%20within%20a%20month%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPrice%20forecast%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EBrent%20trades%20in%20a%20%2480-to-%2490%20per%20barrel%20range%20in%202026%2C%20then%20falls%20to%20%2475%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInvesting%20recommendations%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EMS%20says%20risk%20assets%20will%20outperform%2C%20and%20that%20investors%20should%20go%3A%20overweight%20equities%2C%20equal-weight%20government%20bonds%2C%20and%20underweight%20corporate%20credit%20and%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScenario%202%3A%20Ongoing%20constraints%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOutcome%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E80%25%20of%20tanker%20passage%20resumes%20within%20a%20month%2C%20but%20normalization%20takes%20a%20full%20quarter%2C%20and%20Iran%20retains%20influence%20over%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPrice%20forecast%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3EBrent%20trades%20in%20a%20%24100-to-%24110%20per%20barrel%20range%20in%202026%2C%20then%20falls%20to%20%2480%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EInvesting%20recommendations%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20MS%20says%20to%20lean%20into%20risk%20assets%2C%20but%20expect%20choppy%20trading.%20The%20firm%20says%20investors%20should%20go%3A%20overweight%20equities%20and%20cash%2C%20underw