%20live%20in%20apartments%20where%20balconies%20replace%20courtyards.%20Yet%20the%20sight%20of%20a%20pot%20brimming%20with%20orange%20marigolds%20still%20brings%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlanting%20them%20in%20October%20is%20more%20than%20gardening%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20keeping%20tradition%20alive.%20It%20is%20remembering%20how%20grandmothers%20understood%20seasons%20by%20watching%20the%20sky%2C%20soil%2C%20and%20festivals%20rather%20than%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20plant%20marigolds%20now%20is%20to%20inherit%20their%20wisdom%3A%20to%20let%20gardens%20breathe%20colour%2C%20protect%20other%20plants%20naturally%2C%20and%20welcome%20a%20flower%20that%20has%20walked%20with%20Indian%20households%20for%20centuries.%20When%20October%20comes%2C%20pressing%20a%20few%20marigold%20seeds%20into%20the%20soil%20may%20remind%20you%20why%20your%20grandmother%20always%20did%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20grow%20marigolds%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20your%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20beloved%20tradition%20fade%20out.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264682%2Fmarigold-farmers-jammu-kashmir-maize-crop-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarigolds%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20among%20the%20easiest%20and%20most%20cheerful%20flowers%2C%20and%20you%20can%20grow%20them%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201400px)%20100vw%2C%201400px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2FA-farmer-shows-fresh-marigold-flowers-of-his-fields-in-Gajoth-Village-of-District-Doda-Jammu-and-Kashmir.-1.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22When%20October%20comes%2C%20pressing%20a%20few%20marigold%20seeds%20into%20the%20soil%20may%20remind%20you%20why%20your%20grandmother%20always%20did%20the%20same.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22ht