C%20and%20environmentally%20conscious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20did%20this%20trend%2C%20equal%20parts%20quirky%20and%20sentimental%2C%20take%20root%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20stunning%20creation%20by%20Enchanted%20Threads%2C%20founded%20by%20Ananya%20Malhotra.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496046%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20stunning%20creation%20by%20Enchanted%20Threads%2C%20founded%20by%20Ananya%20Malhotra.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fenchanted_threads._%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnchanted%20Threads%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20garland%20that%20never%20wilts%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Ananya%20Malhotra%2C%20founder%20of%20Enchanted%20Threads%2C%20the%20idea%20sprouted%20from%20a%20simple%20observation.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20were%20already%20preserving%20their%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20resin%20art.%20I%20thought%2C%20why%20not%20preserve%20the%20entire%20thing%20instead%20of%20just%20parts%20of%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20the%20concept%20raised%20eyebrows.%20Could%20yarn%20really%20replace%20the%20fragrance%20and%20grandeur%20of%20roses%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20response%20was%20mixed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ananya%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20people%20loved%20the%20concept%20of%20forever%20sustainable%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20whereas%20others%20still%20preferred%20fresh%20flowers%20because%20of%20their%20elegance.%20It%20took%20time%20for%20people%20to%20warm%20up%2C%20but%20now%20we%E2%80%99re%20seeing%20far%20more%20queries%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20this%20surge%2C%20she%20explains%2C%20comes%20from%20the%20diaspora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMostly%2C%20the%20NRIs%20are%20really%20loving%20the%20concept.%20It%20has%20this%20delicate%2C%20niche%20quality%20and%20connects%20them%20back%20to%20their%20heritage.%20They%20also%20appreciate%20the%20custom%20options%2C%20different%20flowers%2C%20pearls%2C%20and%20colour%20schemes%2C%20which%20allow%20them%20to%20personalise%20in%20a%20way%20fresh%20flowers%20often%20can%E2%80%99t.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335040%2Fgujarat-padma-pareekh-runs-pb-handmades-crochet-handicraft-small-business-senior-citizen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Etakes%20between%2014%20to%2020%20hours%20to%20complete%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20design.%20The%20process%20begins%20with%20careful%20planning%3A%20the%20right%20flower%20size%2C%20the%20right%20colours%2C%20the%20right%20balance%20of%20pearls%20and%20embellishments.%20Once%20the%20prototype%20is%20approved%2C%20her%20team%20of%2025%20underprivileged%20women%20artisans%20from%20Uttarakhand%20gets%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanya%20Setia%E2%80%99s%20Gul%20is%20another%20powerhouse%20of%20sustainability%20where%20beautiful%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20take%20shape.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20piece%20is%20a%20work%20of%20art%20that%20embodies%20the%20beauty%20of%20rural%20India%20and%20the%20passion%20of%20our%20women%20artisans.%20We%20at%20Gul%20Jaipur%20are%20firm%20believers%20in%20the%20virtues%20of%20conscious%20living%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanya.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20closely%20with%20our%20women%20artisans%20to%20guarantee%20that%20they%20receive%20their%20much-deserved%20recognition%20and%20working%20conditions%20while%20creating%20our%20products%20using%20their%20learned%20skill%20sets%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T013413.770_11zon-1756930720-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496049%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETanya%20Setia%E2%80%99s%20Gul%20is%20another%20powerhouse%20of%20sustainability%20where%20beautiful%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20take%20shape.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDHOZUl0NIcI%2F%3Fimg_index%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Gul%20Jaipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20production%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ananya%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20challenge%20is%20timelines.%20Because%20this%20trend%20is%20still%20new%2C%20couples%20often%20place%20orders%20just%20a%20week%20before%20the%20wedding.%20Customisation%20takes%20time%2C%20and%20since%20it%E2%80%99s%20for%20their%20special%20day%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20absolutely%20perfect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20sentiment%2C%20Ananya%20also%20points%20to%20the%20sustainability%20argument.%20Fresh%20flowers%20often%20travel%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20India%20or%20even%20internationally%2C%20requiring%20refrigeration%20and%20transport.%20Crochet%20alternatives%2C%20she%20says%2C%20cut%20down%20this%20carbon%20footprint%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20better%20way%20forward.%20Fresh%20flowers%20end%20up%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F449690%2Fdelhi-zero-waste-colony-navjivan-vihar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egarbage%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewithin%20hours.%20Crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecan%20be%20priced%20in%20the%20same%20range%2C%20and%20you%20can%20keep%20them%20forever%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20lockdown%20hobby%20turns%20into%20forever%20memories%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2018-year-old%20Manya%20Jain%20of%20Knot%20Kisses%2C%20the%20journey%20to%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebegan%20in%20her%20bedroom%20during%20the%202020%20lockdown.%20She%20was%20barely%2013%20when%20she%20picked%20up%20a%20hook%20because%20she%20wanted%20new%20clothes%20and%20her%20mother%20refused%20to%20buy%20them.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20rebellion%20became%20a%20craft%2C%20and%20then%20a%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20taught%20myself%20entirely%20through%20YouTube%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandmother%20used%20to%20crochet%2C%20and%20I%20was%20always%20fascinated.%20With%20time%2C%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leap%20from%20fashion%20accessories%20to%20wedding%20garlands%20came%20unexpectedly.%20At%20a%20Delhi%20event%20where%20she%20had%20set%20up%20a%20stall%2C%20a%20bride-to-be%20asked%20if%20she%20could%20make%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20her%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20moment%20was%20really%20special%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manya%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99d%20always%20imagined%20making%20one%20for%20my%20own%20wedding%20someday.%20To%20actually%20craft%20one%20for%20someone%20else%20felt%20surreal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDGk6a1syDvb%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDGk6a1syDvb%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDGk6a1syDvb%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Knot%20Kisses%20(%40knot.kisses)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20process%20is%20deeply%20collaborative.%20Couples%20share%20references%2C%20colours%2C%20themes%2C%20and%20even%20the%20mood%20they%20want%20to%20create.%20Manya%20sketches%20five%20or%20six%20design%20options%2C%20balancing%20length%2C%20floral%20motifs%2C%20and%20detailing%20before%20she%20begins%20crocheting.%20%E2%80%9CI%20undid%20my%20first%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethree%20times%20before%20it%20felt%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20pair%20takes%20about%20four%20to%20five%20hours%20to%20craft.%20Basic%20designs%20with%20a%20single%20string%20of%20flowers%20and%20beads%20start%20at%20Rs%203%2C500%2C%20while%20customised%20versions%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%209%2C500%20or%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECouples%20can%20choose%20not%20just%20the%20colours%20and%20flowers%2C%20but%20also%20add%20small%20personal%20details.%20%E2%80%9COne%20couple%20wanted%20their%20college%20colours%20included%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%20fell%20in%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20the%20beauty%20of%20crochet%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20saving%20flowers%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20saving%20a%20moment%2C%20a%20story%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20love%20stitched%20by%20hand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F475664%2Fsustainability-mafia-students-climate-startups-climate-solutions-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESustainability%20%3C%2Fa%3Eplays%20a%20role%20here%20too.%20Manya%20prefers%20cotton%20yarn%20for%20its%20lightness%20and%20comfort%2C%20and%20she%20often%20upcycles%20beads%20or%20embellishments%20from%20old%20jewellery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20has%20been%20her%20biggest%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20by%20posting%20crochet%20work%20online.%20Consistency%2C%20sharing%20behind-the-scenes%2C%20connecting%20with%20people%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20orders%20came%20in.%20Now%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20queries%2C%20especially%20for%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20gone%20viral%20overnight%2C%20but%20it%20has%20grown%20steadily.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20keepsake%20that%20is%20full%20of%20soul%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Zainab%20Mukhtyar%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20about%20intimacy%20and%20permanence.%20%E2%80%9CTraditional%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20lovely%2C%20but%20they%20fade%20away%20within%20hours.%20With%20crochet%2C%20you%20can%20preserve%20that%20special%20moment.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20keepsake%20that%20couples%20can%20hold%20on%20to%2C%20just%20like%20their%20memories%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zainab's%20crochet%20brand%20focuses%20on%20the%20emotional%20value%20of%20each%20varmala.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496052%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EZainab%E2%80%99s%20crochet%20brand%20focuses%20on%20the%20emotional%20value%20of%20each%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fzains_story%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZain%E2%80%99s%20Story%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Manya%2C%20Zainab%E2%80%99s%20idea%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20from%20a%20specific%20request.%20It%20was%20born%20out%20of%20her%20own%20reflections%20on%20weddings%20and%20memory.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20one%20moment.%20It%20was%20just%20the%20thought%20that%20you%20could%20preserve%20your%20special%20day%20in%20a%20more%20meaningful%20way.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20began%20curating%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%2C%20she%20says%2C%20has%20been%20steadily%20growing.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20off%20immediately%2C%20but%20now%20I%20get%20new%20queries%20almost%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%20Each%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Etakes%20two%20to%20three%20days%20to%20make%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20number%20of%20flowers%20and%20the%20design.%20She%20uses%20acrylic%20yarn%20and%20adds%20beads%20to%20bind%20the%20flowers%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Zainab%2C%20the%20appeal%20lies%20in%20the%20emotional%20value.%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20goes%20to%20waste.%20The%20flowers%20don%E2%80%99t%20wilt.%20It%E2%80%99s%20handmade%20with%20love%20and%20care%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20couples%20can%20keep%20forever.%20I%20feel%20weddings%20are%20moving%20towards%20more%20sustainable%2C%20mindful%20choices%2C%20and%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Efit%20right%20into%20that.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20how%20sentimental%20they%20are%20and%20full%20of%20soul.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20crochet%2C%20why%20now%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Esays%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20Indian%20weddings%20are%20evolving.%20Once%20notorious%20for%20their%20extravagance%20and%20waste%2C%20younger%20couples%20are%20increasingly%20seeking%20ways%20to%20make%20their%20celebrations%20more%20personal%20and%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20always%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20fresh%20trends%20and%20styles%2C%20so%20when%20I%20came%20across%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20found%20them%20incredibly%20cute%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20could%20create%20a%20buzz%20at%20my%20wedding%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2026-year-old%20Shilpa%2C%20who%20tied%20the%20knot%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20ordered%20white%20%3Cem%3Emogra%3C%2Fem%3E-like%20flowers%20with%20an%20additional%20layer%20of%20crochet%20roses%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20piece%20cost%20me%20around%20Rs%204%2C300.%20The%20varmala%20is%20now%20framed%20in%20my%20living%20room%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20best%20thing%20to%20see%20when%20I%20wake%20up%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20couples%20mindful%20of%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20or%20eager%20for%20keepsakes%2C%20crochet%20varmalas%20offers%20a%20way%20out.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496056%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20couples%20mindful%20of%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20or%20eager%20for%20keepsakes%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoffers%20a%20way%20out.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fzains_story%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZain%E2%80%99s%20Story%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFresh%20flowers%2C%20while%20undeniably%20beautiful%2C%20come%20with%20hidden%20costs%2C%20including%20environmental%2C%20financial%2C%20and%20emotional.%20Hours%20of%20refrigeration%2C%20long-distance%20transport%2C%20and%20thousands%20of%20rupees%20spent%20on%20garlands%20that%20last%20barely%20an%20evening.%20For%20couples%20mindful%20of%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20or%20eager%20for%20keepsakes%2C%20crochet%20offers%20a%20way%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20revivalist%20charm%20to%20it.%20Crochet%2C%20once%20dismissed%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgrandmother%E2%80%99s%20hobby%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20now%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20slow%20fashion%20and%20handmade%20crafts.%20It%20carries%20a%20nostalgia%2C%20a%20tactile%20softness%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20intimacy%20that%20mass-produced%20items%20lack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20is%20the%20Instagram%20effect.%20A%20pastel%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eagainst%20a%20cream%20%3Cem%3Esherwani%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20a%20red%20%3Cem%3Elehenga%20%3C%2Fem%3Emakes%20for%20striking%20visuals%2C%20fuelling%20curiosity%20and%20desire%20among%20wedding%20planners%20and%20couples%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20craft%2C%20a%20community%2C%20a%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20not%20just%20designers%2C%20but%20entire%20communities%20of%20women%20artisans.%20At%20Enchanted%20Threads%2C%20Ananya%20ensures%2030%20percent%20of%20the%20proceeds%20go%20directly%20to%20her%20team%20of%20underprivileged%20women%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20For%20Manya%2C%20it%20has%20been%20about%20collaboration%20with%20fellow%20crochet%20artists%2C%20slowly%20expanding%20from%20a%20solo%20effort%20to%20a%20small%20creative%20team.%20For%20Zainab%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20pouring%20herself%20into%20every%20detail%2C%20bead%20by%20bead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecarries%20within%20it%20not%20just%20threads%20and%20knots%2C%20but%20also%20stories%20of%20empowerment%2C%20patience%2C%20and%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20are%20real.%20Tight%20timelines%2C%20lack%20of%20awareness%2C%20the%20lingering%20preference%20for%20fresh%20flowers%2C%20but%20so%20is%20the%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-instagram%5C%22%3E%3Cd